com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query

Interface ElementQuery<R extends TitanElement,B extends BackendQuery<B>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Query
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphCentricQuery, VertexCentricQuery

    public interface ElementQuery<R extends TitanElement,B extends BackendQuery<B>>
extends Query
    A query that returns TitanElements. This query can consist of multiple sub-queries that together form the desired result set.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
